    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.poster.avif?t=1729034290\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.webm?t=1729034290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.mp4?t=1729034290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/8e5cd3677590d521b527b388234687dc.webp?t=1729034290\" width=512 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Today on The Color Fun Coloring Show they want viewers to help them find out who is breaking into their house. Each new Fear that breaks in will hunt you down! All the show wants to know is what color they show you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/0c480748aab7ae8c33596316394d916b.poster.avif?t=1729034290\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/0c480748aab7ae8c33596316394d916b.webm?t=1729034290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/7e245dd84a0c3246b75f70d762cbdca5.webp?t=1729034290\" width=512 height=25 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Designed for Fear.</strong> Intruders not only can come in at random times but can also be in the places where they know you will be going to. There is a chance that a level just doesn't have any intruders or that those noises coming up the stairs opening the door are either a ghost or an intruder</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a Horror game unlike any other.</strong> Explore the deepest fears that come from The Color Fun Coloring Show.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/6227f205aa3266aa58e324c423a9696e.poster.avif?t=1729034290\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/6227f205aa3266aa58e324c423a9696e.webm?t=1729034290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/7136b35085a478c51295b81bfa0f289e.webp?t=1729034290\" width=512 height=25 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive each night</strong> as Peach wakes you up to play in his horror experience, as you explore your house while being chased by your fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/3a1b6ca31ee500d3f791042ef9372591.webp?t=1729034290\" width=512 height=25 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out why</strong> Peach is making you play his twisted game each night. Delve into the history of The Color Fun Coloring Show and why it came to be.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/c5c6e0421b7bf8b2e9c97640deda39e2.webp?t=1729034290\" width=512 height=25 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each night, you'll play Peaches</strong> twisted game to survive. You must follow Peaches instructions inside the house, find a specific color, and show it to Peach on the TV. But during the night. There are intruders in the house who will wait for you or chase you. Get the color right, and you'll live. Get it wrong, and you're out.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playthrough Time</strong> 25-65min</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Replay-ability</strong> is great with a good amount of randomization to keep every playthrough and level as fresh and scary as possible from random room spawns, intruders, buildings, tv locations and level sequences.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/656f7b5bd6db4a60c99d199abe9de6d8.poster.avif?t=1729034290\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/656f7b5bd6db4a60c99d199abe9de6d8.webm?t=1729034290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245620/extras/6af2acbe4829a2f6ed54345a4d85bea9.webp?t=1729034290\" width=512 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
